<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4322529>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Preserved holotypes of Uroplatus fangorn sp. nov. (ZSM 79/2005) and U. fivehy sp. nov. (ZSM 1721/2012)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4322529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4322523>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Individuals of Uroplatus fangorn sp. nov. photographed in life. A, Male holotype (ZSM 79/2005) from Marojejy. B, C, D, male paratype (ZSM 644/2014) from Andrevorevo. E, F, G, female paratype (UADBA-R 70054 / DRV 6281), from Andrevorevo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4322523/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4322513>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Bayesian inference phylogenetic tree of the Uroplatus ebenaui group based on a 2686 bp alignment of five concatenated mitochondrial and nuclear gene fragments (ND4, 12S rRNA, 16S rRNA, COX1, CMOS). Posterior probability values are shown on the nodes (omitted for most shallow nodes). Uroplatus alluaudi was used as the outgroup (not shown)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4322513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

